org.transitime.db.structs

Class VehicleEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.db.structs.VehicleEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Immutable
 @Entity
public class VehicleEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    For storing events associated with vehicles into log file and into database. Used for situations such as vehicles becoming predictable or unpredictable and specifying why. The resulting information can be mapped out for finding problems.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
